high_descs: Go to the counter.
Pick up the ladle on the counter
Turn and go to the counter by the stove.
Put the ladle on the plate on the counter.
Pick up the plate on the counter.
Turn around and go to the cabinet by the stove.
Put the plate and ladle in the cabinet.
anns.task_desc: Put the ladle with the plate away in the cabinet.

high_descs: Move to the counter in front of you beside the bin.
Pick up the ladle from the counter.
Move to the counter to the left of the stove across from the fridge,
Place the ladle on the plate on the counter.
Pick up the plate from the counter.
Move closer to the stove on the right.
Open the farthest cabinet to the right  on the bottom and place the plate inside and close the door.
anns.task_desc: Put a plate with a ladle on it in the bottom farthest right cabinet to the left of the stove.

high_descs: Turn left and take a step forward, then turn right and walk up to the end of the counter.
Pick up the large metal spoon on the end of the counter.
Turn left and walk forward, then hang a right and begin walking across the room, hang a left and walk up to the small white plate on the counter.
Place the metal spoon on the small white plate handle up.
Pick up the white plate with the spoon on it off of the counter.
Turn around and begin walking to the fridge, then turn around again to face the counter and look down.
Open the rightmost cabinet door and plate the plate with the spoon on it inside.
anns.task_desc: Put a plate with a spoon on it inside a cabinet.

high_descs: Turn a step to your left and then head to the edge of the counter
Pick up the spoon off of the counter
Walk right down the kitchen, then take a left turn to face the kitchen counter
Place the spoon on the plate
Pick up the plate with the spoon on it
Take a step back from where you were standing
Open the cabinet door, place the plate with the spoon on in the cabinet and close the door
anns.task_desc: Put a plate with a spoon on it in the kitchen cabinet

high_descs: Go slightly to the left, then go back to the right to the counter next to the garbage can.
Pick up the ladle that is on the counter.
Go left, then go right, go down towards the other end of the room, go left to the counter directly across from the fridge where the white bowl is.
Put the ladle inside the white bowl.
Pick up the white bowl that is on the counter.
Turn around and back up a little bit from the counter.
Open the cupboard immediately to the left of the stove, put the bowl inside and close the door.
anns.task_desc: Put a bowl with a ladle in it inside a cupboard.
